<i>In Satisfaction's-
guaranteed-ville</i>

24
00:02:48,402 --> 00:02:53,407
<i>In Thneedville,
we don't want to know</i>

25
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:59,496
<i>Where the smog and trash
and chemicals go</i>

26
00:02:59,663 --> 00:03:03,834
<i>I just went swimming,
and now I glow</i>

27
00:03:03,917 --> 00:03:07,504
<i>In Thneedville,
we have fun year round</i>

28
00:03:07,671 --> 00:03:11,007
<i>We surf and snowboard
right in town</i>

29
00:03:11,174 --> 00:03:14,845
<i>We thank the Lord
for all we've got</i>

30
00:03:15,011 --> 00:03:18,682
<i>Including this
brand new parking lot!</i>

31
00:03:18,849 --> 00:03:24,938
<i>Parking lot!</i>

32
00:03:28,441 --> 00:03:31,862
<i>Oh, look, it's Aloysius O'Hare</i>

33
00:03:32,028 --> 00:03:35,407
<i>Aloysius O'Hare</i>

34
00:03:35,657 --> 00:03:39,870
<i>The man who found
a way to sell air</i>

35
00:03:40,245 --> 00:03:42,372
<i>And became a zillionaire</i>

36
